#linked-accounts
  %h1{style: "margin-top:0px"} Linked Accounts
  %p.lead 
    Trym can link to the acounts below and find recurring charges for you. Link all your accounts and we'll alert you when we find new recurring charges or if your recurring charges change in price.
  %ul
    %li
      =render 'shared/security_notice'
    %li
      Trym scans linked accounts every day and alerts you if we find new charges which look recurring
    %li You can always unlink any of your accounts at any time.  Visit that linked account by clicking the button marked "Linked" and then click the button marked "unlink".

  .paragraph-spacer
  =render 'shared/financial_institutions'

  .text-center
    %small
      Any accounts that you've linked will show as "Linked".  If your account is being updated, they'll show as "syncing" or "analyzing" until the update is complete.  This usually takes less thank two minutes.
